      <div class="section-body">
        <div class="cs-split">
          <div class="cs-prose">
            <p>Following the initial launch, Dialpad tripled investment in the initiative. The team expanded from 50 to 150 people. Design grew from 1 to 8 designers under my oversight.</p>
            <p>My role shifted from sole contributor to system steward — while still maintaining IC ownership on high-impact areas.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-split-stat" aria-hidden="true">1→8</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="cs-subheading">Scaling the Design System for Agents</h3>
        <div class="cs-prose">
          <p>As scope expanded, the product evolved into a broader AI platform, including:</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="cs-list">
          <li>Visual drag-and-drop agent orchestration tools</li>
          <li>Integration model for external systems (including MCP servers)</li>
          <li>Expanded safety and governance controls</li>
          <li>Automated evaluation and improvement workflows</li>
          <li>Analytics and performance monitoring</li>
          <li>Versioning and iteration systems</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

